# Mobile viewport

Read [`docs/mobile-viewport.md`](../docs/mobile-viewport.md) before changing layout shell, fixed bars, or modals.

- `viewport-fit=cover` + `env(safe-area-inset-*)` with `max()` fallback
- Fixed/sticky elements pad themselves
- Min 44px touch targets; test iPhone **standalone PWA**, not only desktop DevTools
- Never `user-scalable=no`

Layout bugs → **Mobile Viewport Agent** (`agents/mobile-viewport-agent.md`).
